```tsx\n<div className=\"columns-3 gap-2\">\n  {preview.map((photo) => (\n    ...\n```\n\n(Remove the outer `<Link>` and its closing tag. Keep the inner photo `<div>` elements and everything inside them. Remove the `key={i}` → use `key={photo.src}` from Fix 2 Issue 1 above.)\n\n---\n\n### After all edits:\n\nRun `cd \"e:/GitProject/awesome-big-V\" && npx tsc --noEmit` — must pass with zero errors.\n\nThen commit:\n```bash\ngit add components/home/ExperiencePreview.tsx components/home/PhotoPreview.tsx\ngit commit -m \"fix(home): guard empty data access, stable photo keys, remove anonymous link wrapper\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Status reporting:\nEnd your response with exactly one of:\n- `STATUS: DONE`\n- `STATUS: DONE_WITH_CONCERNS`\n- `STATUS: NEEDS_CONTEXT`\n- `STATUS: BLOCKED`","model":"sonnet","mode":"auto"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FLF84bEKAMy8saJHKJwx2G"}
[2026-04-23 17:32:49] TOOL   | unknown | raw: {"session_id":"f28224a5-c59d-4651-b843-1cf5874f0d71","transcript_path":"C:\\Users\\wuyin\\.claude\\projects\\e--GitProject-awesome-big-V\\f28224a5-c59d-4651-b843-1cf5874f0d71.jsonl","cwd":"E:\\GitProject\\awesome-big-V","permission_mode":"acceptEdits","hook_event_name":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Agent","tool_input":{"description":"Task 5: Career page components","prompt":"You are implementing Task 5 of a personal portfolio website for Vincent Ng. The project is at `e:/GitProject/awesome-big-V`. It uses Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v3. The dev server is NOT running — do NOT start it.\n\n**Context:** Tasks 1–4 are complete. The data files exist at `data/experience.ts` (exports `experience`, `education`, `certifications`) and `data/projects.ts` (exports `projects`). The design tokens are: `cream`, `ink`, `ink-body`, `ink-muted`, `parchment` (colors), `font-serif` (Playfair Display), `font-sans` (Inter), `rounded-card` (6px). No `'use client'` needed for any of these — they are pure Server Components.\n\n**Your task:** Create the Career page components and `app/career/page.tsx`.\n\n---\n\n### Files to create:\n\n**Create `components/career/ExperienceTimeline.tsx`:**\n```tsx\nimport { experience } from '@/data/experience'\n\nexport default function ExperienceTimeline() {\n  return (\n    <section className=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 border-b border-parchment\">\n      <p className=\"font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[2px] text-ink-muted mb-10\">Experience</p>\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col\">\n        {experience.map((entry, i) => (\n          <div key={entry.company} className=\"flex gap-6\">\n            {/* Timeline spine */}\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center w-4 flex-shrink-0 pt-1\">\n              <div className={`w-2 h-2 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 ${i === 0 ? 'bg-ink' : i === 1 ? 'bg-ink-muted' : 'bg-parchment border border-ink-muted'}`} />\n              {i < experience.length - 1 && (\n                <div className=\"w-px flex-1 bg-parchment mt-1\" />\n              )}\n            </div>\n            {/* Content */}\n            <div className={`flex-1 ${i < experience.length - 1 ? 'pb-10' : ''}`}>\n              <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-baseline gap-1 mb-2\">\n                <span className=\"font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-ink\">\n                  {entry.company} — {entry.role}\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"font-sans text-xs text-ink-muted flex-shrink-0\">{entry.period}</span>\n              </div>\n              {entry.stack.length > 0 && (\n                <p className=\"font-sans text-xs text-ink-muted mb-3 tracking-wide\">\n                  {entry.stack.join(' · ')}\n                </p>\n              )}\n              <ul className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n                {entry.bullets.map((bullet, j) => (\n                  <li key={j} className=\"font-sans text-sm text-ink-body leading-relaxed\">\n                    • {bullet}\n                  </li>\n                ))}\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  )\n}\n```\n\nNOTE: Use `key={entry.company}` (stable string) instead of `key={i}` on the outer `div`. Use `key={j}` on the bullet `<li>` is acceptable since the bullets array is static per entry and never reordered.\n\n**Create `components/career/ProjectCard.tsx`:**\n```tsx\nimport Image from 'next/image'\nimport type { Project } from '@/data/projects'\n\nexport default function ProjectCard({ project }: { project: Project }) {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"border border-parchment rounded-card overflow-hidden bg-cream flex flex-col sm:flex-row\">\n      {/* Text — left */}\n      <div className=\"flex-1 p-6 flex flex-col justify-center\">\n        <h3 className=\"font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1.5\">{project.title}</h3>\n        <p className=\"font-sans text-xs text-ink-muted mb-3 tracking-wide\">\n          {project.stack.join(' · ')}\n        </p>\n        <p className=\"font-sans text-sm text-ink-body leading-relaxed\">{project.description}</p>\n      </div>\n      {/* Image — right */}\n      <div className=\"sm:w-52 sm:flex-shrink-0 h-40 sm:h-auto relative bg-parchment\">\n        <Image\n          src={project.image}\n          alt={project.title}\n          fill\n          className=\"object-cover\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 208px\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n```\n\nNOTE: Use `bg-cream` instead of `bg-white` for consistency with design tokens. Remove the `onError` handler — it's not needed (missing images show the `bg-parchment` placeholder naturally).\n\n**Create `components/career/SkillsEducation.tsx`:**\n```tsx\nimport { education, certifications } from '@/data/experience'\n\nconst skills = [\n  'TypeScript', 'JavaScript', 'Python',\n  'Node.js', 'Next.js', 'React', 'Tailwind CSS',\n  'PostgreSQL', 'Redis', 'REST APIs',\n  'GCP', 'AWS', 'Docker', 'CI/CD',\n  'RAG', 'LLM', 'Agentic Systems', 'VectorDB',\n]\n\nexport default function SkillsEducation() {\n  return (\n    <section className=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16\">\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12\">\n        {/* Skills */}\n        <div>\n          <p className=\"font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[2px] text-ink-muted mb-6\">Skills</p>\n          <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n            {skills.map((skill) => (\n              <span\n                key={skill}\n                className=\"font-sans text-xs text-ink-body border border-parchment rounded-sm px-2.5 py-1\"\n              >\n                {skill}\n              </span>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        {/* Education */}\n        <div>\n          <p className=\"font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[2px] text-ink-muted mb-6\">Education</p>\n          <p className=\"font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1\">{education.institution}</p>\n          <p className=\"font-sans text-sm text-ink-body leading-relaxed mb-1\">{education.degree}</p>\n          <p className=\"font-sans text-xs text-ink-muted mb-5\">{education.period}</p>\n          <p className=\"font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[2px] text-ink-muted mb-3\">Certifications</p>\n          {certifications.map((cert) => (\n            <p key={cert.name} className=\"font-sans text-sm text-ink-body leading-relaxed\">\n              {cert.name} · {cert.year}\n            </p>\n          ))}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n**Create `app/career/page.tsx`:**\n```tsx\nimport ExperienceTimeline from '@/components/career/ExperienceTimeline'\nimport ProjectCard from '@/components/career/ProjectCard'\nimport SkillsEducation from '@/components/career/SkillsEducation'\nimport { projects } from '@/data/projects'\n\nexport default function CareerPage() {\n  return (\n    <>\n      {/* Page header */}\n      <div className=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-14 border-b border-parchment\">\n        <p className=\"font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[2px] text-ink-muted mb-4\">Career</p>\n        <h1 className=\"font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-normal text-ink leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4\">\n          Experience &amp; Projects\n        </h1>\n        <p className=\"font-sans text-sm text-ink-body leading-relaxed max-w-lg\">\n          Full-stack developer with a focus on AI systems, cloud infrastructure, and production SaaS.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <ExperienceTimeline />\n\n      {/* Projects */}\n      <section className=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 border-b border-parchment\">\n        <p className=\"font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[2px] text-ink-muted mb-10\">\n          Featured Projects\n        </p>\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-4\">\n          {projects.map((project) => (\n            <ProjectCard key={project.title} project={project} />\n          ))}\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <SkillsEducation />\n    </>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### After creating all files:\n\nRun `cd \"e:/GitProject/awesome-big-V\" && npx tsc --noEmit` — must pass with zero errors. Fix any type errors.\n\nCommit:\n```bash\ngit add components/career/ app/career/\ngit commit -m \"feat: add Career page with timeline, project cards, and skills\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Status reporting:\nEnd with exactly one of:\n- `STATUS: DONE`\n- `STATUS: DONE_WITH_CONCERNS`\n- `STATUS: NEEDS_CONTEXT`\n- `STATUS: BLOCKED`","model":"sonnet","mode":"auto"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FQK9AFmnXMrpqrpKgakW9c"}
