`\n\n**Issue (Important):** Certifications are rendered as `<p>` elements — semantically they are a list.\n\nFind the certifications mapping:\n```tsx\n{certifications.map((cert) => (\n  <p key={cert.name} className=\"font-sans text-sm text-ink-body leading-relaxed\">\n    {cert.name} · {cert.year}\n  </p>\n))}\n```\n\nReplace with:\n```tsx\n<ul className=\"list-none flex flex-col gap-1\">\n  {certifications.map((cert) => (\n    <li key={cert.name} className=\"font-sans text-sm text-ink-body leading-relaxed\">\n      {cert.name} · {cert.year}\n    </li>\n  ))}\n</ul>\n```\n\n---\n\n### After all edits:\n\nRun `cd \"e:/GitProject/awesome-big-V\" && npx tsc --noEmit` — must pass with zero errors.\n\nCommit:\n```bash\ngit add components/career/ProjectCard.tsx components/career/ExperienceTimeline.tsx components/career/SkillsEducation.tsx\ngit commit -m \"fix(career): fill image height, alt text, list semantics, stable timeline keys\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Status reporting:\nEnd with exactly one of:\n- `STATUS: DONE`\n- `STATUS: DONE_WITH_CONCERNS`\n- `STATUS: NEEDS_CONTEXT`\n- `STATUS: BLOCKED`","model":"sonnet","mode":"auto"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01S7hzg3kNTurD4fhdvsR99v"}
