r Components)\n- `react-masonry-css` pinned to exact version `1.0.16`\n- Section labels changed to `<h2>`/`<h3>` for document outline\n- Lightbox has focus trap via `tabIndex={-1}` + `useRef` auto-focus\n- Project images show `bg-parchment` placeholder when image files aren't present yet\n- `photos` array starts empty — graceful fallback renders \"Photos coming soon.\"\n\n**What to check:**\n1. Cross-cutting concerns: consistency of design tokens, font usage, spacing patterns across all files\n2. TypeScript integrity: no `any`, correct types, clean interfaces across the data/component boundary\n3. Correctness: any crashes, bugs, or runtime errors that would affect a first-time visitor\n4. Accessibility: semantic HTML, ARIA correctness, keyboard navigation\n5. Next.js best practices: correct use of `next/image`, `next/link`, metadata, client/server split\n\n**Severity levels:** Critical (must fix), Important (should fix), Suggestion (optional)\n\nWrite a final report. If there are Critical or Important issues, list them specifically (file + line). End with Approved or Needs Changes.","subagent_type":"superpowers:code-reviewer","model":"opus"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XraYH8vaoM2gDhe8w6fXE1"}
